=Treasures Around=

22
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:39,700
=Episode 15=

23
00:01:46,900 --> 00:01:49,020
You need the medicine to get better.

24
00:01:57,260 --> 00:01:58,740
Here. Just one sip.

25
00:02:08,940 --> 00:02:09,780
Let me.

26
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:26,700
Is it sweet?

27
00:02:27,340 --> 00:02:28,180
Yes.

28
00:02:39,180 --> 00:02:40,820
Still thinking about the raw stones?

29
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:44,180
No.

30
00:02:44,780 --> 00:02:45,860
No?

31
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:48,380
Look how furrowed your brows are.

32
00:03:10,740 --> 00:03:11,620
Actually,

33
00:03:12,180 --> 00:03:14,060
I am worried about the raw stones.

34
00:03:14,780 --> 00:03:16,060
But when I see you,

35
00:03:16,580 --> 00:03:17,420
I feel

36
00:03:17,740 --> 00:03:19,060
there's no need to worry.

37
00:03:19,940 --> 00:03:22,620
We survived prison.

38
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:25,580
This small issue with the stones

39
00:03:27,180 --> 00:03:28,460
is nothing.

40
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:35,980
As long as we are together,

41
00:03:36,620 --> 00:03:38,020
we'll find a way.

42
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:58,440
♪Moonlight is reflected in the water,
stars fill the sky♪

43
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:02,140
Why didn't you use this just now?

44
00:04:04,340 --> 00:04:06,900
It's sweeter than candied fruit.

45
